<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>专业选择 on 📖 爱分享读书</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/tags/%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9/</link><description>Recent content in 专业选择 on 📖 爱分享读书</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 01 Jul 2025 09:30:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ishareread.com/tags/%E4%B8%93%E4%B8%9A%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>计算机专业遇冷、法学分数逆势大涨：从《创新者的窘境》看为什么越热门的专业越危险</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/posts/2025-07-01-innovator-dilemma-major-choice/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Jul 2025 09:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/posts/2025-07-01-innovator-dilemma-major-choice/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;你有没有这种感觉：选专业就像炒股票，你以为是抄底，结果抄在了山腰；你以为追的是风口，结果风停了才发现自己站在风眼里。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;去年这时候，我一个朋友家的孩子，分数够上985的计算机专业，全家激动得差点放鞭炮。报志愿的时候，孩子他爸拍着胸脯说：&amp;ldquo;学计算机！互联网大厂，年薪30万起步，妥妥的！&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>